casebody.data:
STATE of Missouri, Respondent,
v.
Joshua Robert URBAN, Appellant. WD 81894 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: July 30, 2019 Ellen Flottman, Columbia, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Nathan Aquino, Jefferson City, MO, Counsel for Respondent. Before Division Three: Gary D. Witt, P.J., Edward R. Ardini, and Thomas N. Chapman, JJ.

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Joshua Urban appeals his convictions following a jury trial in the Circuit Court of Callaway County on two counts of statutory sodomy in the first degree. On appeal, Urban argues that the trial court plainly erred in allowing the testimony of a forensic interviewer that he contends improperly bolstered the credibility of the victim. We affirm. Rule 30.25(b).
